>肉体も<Ruby={2:2}い>要らぬ！","USen":"My body... My mind... Everything!"},{"id":8174,"index":16,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_014_b","CNzh":"我要你们陪我一起堕入地狱！！","TWzh":"就算我死了，也要拖你們一起下地獄！","JPja":"<Ruby={4:6}きさま>貴様らを<Ruby={4:6}じごく>地獄の<Ruby={2:4}みち>道<Ruby={2:2}づ>連れに","USen":"I'll sacrifice it all to destroy you..."},{"id":8175,"index":17,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_015_b","CNzh":"让这个世界在无尽的黑暗中迎来终焉！！","TWzh":"讓永恆的黑暗終結這個世界吧！！","JPja":"<Ruby={4:8}えいごう>永劫の<Ruby={2:4}やみ>闇で <Ruby={4:6}せかい>世界を<Ruby={2:2}お>終わらせてくれるわ！！","USen":"and cast this world into eternal night!"},{"id":8176,"index":18,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_016_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":8177,"index":19,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_017_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":8178,"index":20,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_018_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":8179,"index":21,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_019_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":8180,"index":22,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_020_b","CNzh":"林克！","TWzh":"林克！","JPja":"リンク！","USen":"Link!"},{"id":8181,"index":23,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_021_b","CNzh":"林克！","TWzh":"林克！","JPja":"リンク！","USen":"Link!"},{"id":8182,"index":24,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_022_b","CNzh":"林克！","TWzh":"林克！","JPja":"リンク！","USen":"Link!"},{"id":8183,"index":25,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_023_b","CNzh":"林克！","TWzh":"林克！","JPja":"リンク！","USen":"Link!"},{"id":8184,"index":26,"key":"Dm_GA_0016_Text_024_b","CNzh":"林克！","TWzh":"林克！","JPja":"リンク！","USen":"Link!"}]}